OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1783774108
OL,3,CKing gives 'very well behaved' penguin
OL,4,Ca health check at London Zoo
OL,6,FThe King used a stethoscope to help
OL,7,Fgive a "very well behaved" penguin a
OL,8,Fhealth check during a trip to London
OL,9,FZoo.
OL,11,FCharles, who was accompanied by the
OL,12,FQueen, braved the baking sun and
OL,13,Fjoined zoo vet Stefan Saverimuttu as
OL,14,Fhe checked over a Humboldt penguin
OL,15,Fduring the visit in Camden on Thursday.
OL,17,FDozens of penguins, about two feet
OL,18,Ftall, gathered to greet to royals as
OL,19,Fthe couple approached their enclosure.
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
