PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1783774108
OL,3,CKing gives 'very well behaved' penguin
OL,4,Ca health check at London Zoo
OL,6,FCrouching down, Charles used a red
OL,7,Fstethoscope to check the heartbeat of
OL,8,Fa penguin named Lannister as the bird
OL,9,Fpatiently sat perched on a rock.
OL,11,FCamilla, using a blue stethoscope,
OL,12,Falso bent down to join in.
OL,14,F"Lannister sounded perfect and
OL,15,FLannister was very well behaved for
OL,16,Fthe King and the Queen," Mr
OL,17,FSaverimuttu said.
OL,19,F"They're very endearing," the King
OL,20,Fsaid about the birds.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@XO]{D@AOU{D@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1783774108
OL,3,CKing gives 'very well behaved' penguin
OL,4,Ca health check at London Zoo
OL,6,FAsked how the couple's veterinary
OL,7,Fskills had been, the vet said Charles
OL,8,Fand Camilla had taken to it "very
OL,9,Fwell".
OL,11,F"Both of them were really enthusiastic
OL,12,Fabout the penguins," he added.
OL,14,F"Penguins have a bit of a beak on them
OL,15,Fso I think if you've never met one
OL,16,Fbefore, they might be a bit
OL,17,Fintimidating, but neither the King or
OL,18,Fthe Queen was intimidated in the
OL,19,Fslightest and they went straight in
OL,20,Fand gave it a go and they did really
OL,21,Fwell."
OL,26,@pD@]OUqD@EO]sD@AOUtD@TO]vD@AOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1783774108
OL,3,CKing gives 'very well behaved' penguin
OL,4,Ca health check at London Zoo
OL,6,FThe pair also took part in laser
OL,7,Ftraining exercises used to encourage
OL,8,Fand observe movements in the penguins
OL,9,Fincluding swimming and diving.
OL,11,FThe laser pointers mimic the sparkling
OL,12,Fscales of fish, which penguins are
OL,13,Fknown to chase, and allow vets to spot
OL,14,Fany health concerns.
OL,16,FStanding next to a glass wall with a
OL,17,Fview into the blue pool, Charles and
OL,18,FCamilla, tried unsuccessfully for a
OL,19,Fcouple of minutes to capture the
OL,20,Fpenguins' attention.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1783774108
OL,3,CKing gives 'very well behaved' penguin
OL,4,Ca health check at London Zoo
OL,6,FOne penguin eventually swam up to the
OL,7,FKing's laser pointer as he laughed and
OL,8,Fexclaimed: "That's the only one that's
OL,9,Fnoticing."
OL,11,FCharles wore a blue suit with an
OL,12,Fanimal-themed tie and sunglasses,
OL,13,Fwhile Camilla, carrying a cream
OL,14,Fparasol, chose a white Fiona Clare
OL,15,Fdress adorned with wildlife including
OL,16,Felephants and deer.
OL,26,@pD@LOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
