OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1783774108
OL,3,CKing gives 'very well behaved' penguin
OL,4,Ca health check at London Zoo
OL,6,FDuring the trip, which celebrated the
OL,7,F200th anniversary of the Zoological
OL,8,FSociety of London (ZSL) conservation
OL,9,Fcharity, the couple paused to meet a
OL,10,FGalapagos tortoise named Polly and
OL,11,Fhelp feed her some snacks.
OL,13,FThe 31-year-old tortoise was presented
OL,14,Fwith a watermelon decorated with the
OL,15,Fnumber 200 and flowers.
OL,17,FUsing metal tongs, the Queen fed some
OL,18,Fof the greenery to Polly while the
OL,19,FKing offered her some leaves by hand.
OL,26,@rD@Drp
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1783774108
OL,3,CKing gives 'very well behaved' penguin
OL,4,Ca health check at London Zoo
OL,6,FPolly largely ignored the King's
OL,7,Foffering prompting Charles to jokingly
OL,8,Fask her keeper whether the tortoise
OL,9,Fwas on a "diet".
OL,11,FIn the zoo's Tiny Giants area, Charles
OL,12,Fspoke to staff about the conservation
OL,13,Fwork done by the ZSL to protect
OL,14,FPartula tree snails from extinction
OL,15,Fafter they were wiped out by an
OL,16,Finvasive carnivorous snail species.
OL,18,FAsked whether he would like to paint
OL,19,Fone of the tiny creatures, the King
OL,20,Flaughed and said: "I've painted a few
OL,21,Fthings in my time but never a snail."
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@OO]|D@SOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1783774108
OL,3,CKing gives 'very well behaved' penguin
OL,4,Ca health check at London Zoo
OL,6,FHolding a small paint brush, Charles
OL,7,Fplaced a dot of purple paint on two of
OL,8,Fthe snail's shells which will help to
OL,9,Ftrack them once they are released into
OL,10,Fthe wild in French Polynesia.
OL,12,F"So this is special snail varnish is
OL,13,Fit?" the King joked.
OL,15,FThe visit was Charles's first tour of
OL,16,Fthe zoo as the ZSL's patron, having
OL,17,Fvisited the attraction for the first
OL,18,Ftime as a one-year-old to see Brumas,
OL,19,Fa new born polar bear cub.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@DO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
