OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1783774108
OL,3,CKing gives 'very well behaved' penguin
OL,4,Ca health check at London Zoo
OL,6,FSince 1828, every monarch has been
OL,7,Fpatron of the society.
OL,9,FThe zoo was founded by the ZSL that
OL,10,Fyear in London's Regent's Park,
OL,11,Fbecoming the world's first scientific
OL,12,Fzoo.
OL,14,FDuring the tour, the couple heard
OL,15,Fabout the creation of a new wildlife
OL,16,Fcentre, announced by ZSL to mark the
OL,17,Fanniversary.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1783774108
OL,3,CKing gives 'very well behaved' penguin
OL,4,Ca health check at London Zoo
OL,6,FThe centre will be used to investigate
OL,7,Fdiseases in animals, train wildlife
OL,8,Fvets, track how diseases spread
OL,9,Fbetween species and support
OL,10,Fconservation projects around the world
OL,11,Fas well as providing new veterinary
OL,12,Ffacilities for the animals at ZSL's
OL,13,Ftwo zoos ` London and Whipsnade.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/10
